            <div type="a">
                <column>1</column>
                <head>Thanksgiving Sermon Delivered by Rev. John Ault, in St. Thomas, November
                    29,1860.</head>
                <origin/>
                <commentary/>
                <excerpt/>
                <transcript/>
                <trailer/>
                <names>
                    <name>
                        <ln>Ault</ln>
                        <fn>John</fn>
                        <sf/>
                        <pf>Rev.</pf>
                    </name>
                </names>
                <summary>He preached that the present national crisis is due to: immorality,
                    corruption, disregard to law and order, a spirit of recklessness. Reinstating
                    Christianity in the home and in the government will bring about peace.</summary>
                <note/>
                <look/>
            </div>
